{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Russian Army-- the Russians give an ultimatum for Romania to surrender the Eastern provinces of Bessarabia and Bukovina.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father, he was in the Romanian Army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was at one time in the Romanian Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He was an artillery man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was called in to-- he was called in because the Russians gave an ultimatum to surrender those provinces.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember seeing my father off from the village, and he went into the army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But of course, no war broke out, because when the ultimatum expired, the Russians, they came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They say they came in planes and the Romanian Army surrendered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they withdrew from Bessarabia and Bukovina, and they gave it over to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The Romanian government blamed the Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They claimed that the Jews were a fifth column in the country, and they were supposedly allied with the Communists to take over those provinces.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So anti-Semitism started to raise its ugly head very badly in Romania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In the meantime, France fell.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Romania didn't have no allies, so she made an alliance with Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Hungary was an ally of Germany all the time because it was part of the Austro-Hungarian empire once.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So the Hungarians put claim to the province of Transylvania, of Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And those two people, the Romanians and the Hungarians, they're blood enemies, and they were ready to go to war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they met in Vienna, which is called the Vienna Diktat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Ribbentrop was there and Ciano from Italy, and they took Transylvania and they divide it in half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The northern part of Transylvania was ceded to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And this was in August, 1940, around there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Maybe in July, August 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now, at this point, the Hungarian Army came in and took over the northern part of Transylvania, where my village was located.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
